      <div class="frontpagecontent">
         
        <p><strong>Pendle Hill</strong> is a Quaker study, retreat, and conference center welcoming all for Spirit-led learning and community, located in <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Pendle+Hill/@40.048643,-75.211029,10z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x89c6e9b5f0e3afd1:0xfd4208206dc37096?hl=en" target="_blank">Wallingford, Pennsylvania</a>.</p>
<hr />
<h2>Two-to-One Challenge Match – Triple Your Impact!</h2>
<p>Your gift can have three times the impact during Pendle Hill&#8217;s <strong>Fall Annual Fund 2-to-1 $25,000 Challenge Match!</strong></p>
<p>Click <a href="http://pendlehill.org/support/" target="_blank">here</a> to read more.</p>
<hr />
<p><!--Think about your charitable giving in a different way:

<ul>
 	
<li><span style="color: #000000;" "font-size:14pt;">Your gift to the Annual Fund is automatic each month</span></li>


&nbsp;
 	
<li><span style="color: #000000;" "font-size:14pt;">It's an easy and affordable way to make your support go further and promote sustainability</span></li>


</ul>


Simply choose <a href="http://pendlehill.org/support/your-support-matters/contact-support-recurring-donation/">Make a Recurring Donation</a> when you donate.

You are investing in our vision to create peace with justice in the world by transforming lives. Thank you!

<a href="http://pendlehill.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/sustaining-donors-matrix.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-9012 size-full" title="sustaining donors matrix" src="https://pendlehill.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/sustaining-donors-matrix.jpg" alt="sustaining donors matrix" width="547" height="450" srcset="https://pendlehill.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/sustaining-donors-matrix.jpg 547w, https://pendlehill.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/sustaining-donors-matrix-300x247.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" /></a>--></p>
 
